Sentencas: We report the world smallest tubular solid oxide fuel cell - needle-type micro SOFCs applicable to micro power devices.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices

Sentencas: The anode-supported cell was prepared using cost effective, conventional extrusion and dip-coating techniques.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices

Sentencas: The diameter of the needle-type cell is 0.4 mm, consisting of NiO-Gd doped Ceria (GDC) for anode (under 100 mu m thick), GDC for electrolyte (8 mu m thick), and (La, Sr) (Co, Fe)O-3 - GDC for cathode.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices

Sentencas: The cell performances of 80, 160 and 300 mW cm(-2) at 450 degrees C, 500 degrees C, and 550 degrees C, respectively, were obtained using a simple current collection method with wet H-2 fuel.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices

Sentencas: Impedance analysis indicated that the SOFC has a potential to be improved by optimizing the current collection method.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices

Sentencas: Bundle concept using the SOFCs with the packing density of 100 cells in 1 cm(3) was also proposed.
Titulo: Fabrication of needle-type micro SOFCs for micro power devices
